videos.description: Michigan State RB L.J. Scott catches a pass in the flat and runs 64 yards downfield to give the Spartans an early lead over Ohio State.
videos.headline: L.J. Scott races 64 yards for first TD of game

videos.description: Ohio State QB J.T. Barrett throws a pass over the middle of the field to Curtis Samuel for a 24-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Barrett lofts one up to Samuel for 24-yard score

videos.description: Michigan State fans wearing reindeer heads are in attendance to support the Spartans.
videos.headline: Santa's reindeer in attendance at OSU-MSU

videos.description: Michigan State RB L.J. Scott rushes through a hole in Ohio State's defensive line and runs downfield 61 yards before being brought down.
videos.headline: Scott breaks free for 61-yard run

videos.description: Tyler O'Connor pass intercepted by Chris Worley return for no gain to the MchSt 37
videos.headline: T. O'Connor pass intercepted by C. Worley

videos.description: Ohio State RB Mike Weber loses the football in the red zone, and it is recovered by Michigan State to end the Buckeyes' drive.
videos.headline: Michigan State ends Ohio State's drive recovering a fumble

videos.description: Michigan State head coach Mark Dantonio talks about his teams defensive success in the first half
videos.headline: Michigan State head coach Mark Dantonio talks about his teams defensive success in the first half

videos.description: Ohio State's Tyler Durbin hits a 39-yard field goal to even the score at 10.
videos.headline: Ohio State pulls even with 39-yard field goal

videos.description: Michael Geiger 28-yard FG GOOD
videos.headline: Michigan State pulls ahead with 28-yard field goal

videos.description: Ohio State head coach Urban Meyer talks about his teams need to play their style of football
videos.headline: Ohio State head coach Urban Meyer talks about his teams need to play their style of football

videos.description: Ohio State RB Mike Weber runs four yards up the gut into the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Weber punches it in with 4-yard TD run

videos.description: Michigan State RB L.J. Scott avoids an Ohio State defender by hurdling over him for the first down. However, the play would be called back due to the Spartans being penalized for too many men on the field.
videos.headline: L.J. Scott hurdles OSU defender

videos.description: Chris Frey run for 25-yards to the OhSt 37 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Michigan State fools Ohio State with fake punt

videos.description: Michigan State RB L.J. Scott scores on a 1-yard touchdown run to bring the Spartans within a point of tying the game.
videos.headline: L.J. Scott rushes into end zone for 1-yard score

videos.description: After L.J. Scott's 1-yard touchdown run, Michigan State decides to go for the lead, but Ohio State intercepts a pass in the end zone to maintain its one-point lead over the Spartans.
videos.headline: Michigan State denied on two-point conversion

videos.headline: Ohio State QB J.T. Barrett talks about the teams approach to the weather and a look ahead to their next game against rival Michigan

videos.description: Ohio State head coach Urban Meyer talks about his teams defensive performance in their 17-16 win over Michigan State
videos.headline: Ohio State head coach Urban Meyer talks about his teams defensive performance in their 17-16 win over Michigan State

videos.description: Michigan State QB Tyler O'Connor throws a wobbly pass that is picked off by Ohio State CB Gareon Conley, sealing the Buckeyes' 17-16 victory over the Spartans.
